straight at me.

00:15:13.780 --> 00:15:19.690
The cruel moon decides to make
an appearance right now right

00:15:19.690 --> 00:15:24.410
over the place where we made out.

00:15:25.510 --> 00:16:37.040
[ Guitar and Singing ]

00:16:37.040 --> 00:16:38.640
So, Blade, I think he's had it.

00:16:38.640 --> 00:16:41.850
