00:17:25.650 --> 00:17:31.090
So he's going to leave the
jungle, that's what he calls LA.

00:17:31.090 --> 00:17:36.820
And he's going to West
Africa, a country named Ghana.

00:17:36.820 --> 00:17:40.980
Beautiful country that
